import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch } from "react-router-dom"

import "./index.css"
import { App } from "./App"

ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <Router>
      <Switch>
        <>
          <App />
        </>
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  </React.StrictMode>,

  document.getElementById("root")
)
